{"schemaVersion":1,"bookId":"situational-15000","unitId":"scene-208","title":"会议记录","sectionId":"chapter-09","sectionTitle":"遇见职场“大红人”","pageStart":1033,"pageEnd":1037,"extractionMethod":"text-layer","wordEntryCount":22,"duplicateEntryCount":14,"pages":[{"number":1033,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"208 会议记录"},{"type":"section","text":"Step1 场景词"},{"type":"entry","text":"conference [ˈkɒnfərəns]","headword":"conference"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.会议"},{"type":"note","text":"◎conference call电话会议/conference centre 会议中心"},{"type":"entry","text":"group meeting 小组会议","headword":"group meeting"},{"type":"entry","text":"finance meeting 财务会议","headword":"finance meeting"},{"type":"entry","text":"scheduled [ˈskedʒuːld]","headword":"scheduled"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.已安排的"},{"type":"entry","text":"meeting name 会议名称","headword":"meeting name"},{"type":"entry","text":"attendance [əˈtendəns]","headword":"attendance"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.出席人数；出席，参加"},{"type":"note","text":"◎in attendance出席"}]},{"number":1034,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"take notes 做笔记","headword":"take notes"},{"type":"entry","text":"recording [rɪˈkɔːdɪŋ]","headword":"recording"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.录音"},{"type":"note","text":"◎recording equipment录音设备"},{"type":"entry","text":"attentive [əˈtentɪv]","headword":"attentive"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.注意的，留意的；照顾周到的"},{"type":"note","text":"◎be attentive to注意；照应/attentive service周到的服务"},{"type":"entry","text":"absorbed [əbˈzɔːbd]","headword":"absorbed"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.全神贯注的"},{"type":"note","text":"◎absorbed in全神贯注于…"}]},{"number":1035,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"in conclusion 总之","headword":"in conclusion"},{"type":"entry","text":"productive [prəˈdʌktɪv]","headword":"productive"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.富有成效的"},{"type":"note","text":"◎productive efficiency生产效率"},{"type":"entry","text":"come to a close 渐进尾声","headword":"come to a close"}]},{"number":1036,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"at the end of 在…的结尾","headword":"at the end of"},{"type":"entry","text":"sum up 总结","headword":"sum up"},{"type":"entry","text":"as a result 结果","headword":"as a result"},{"type":"entry","text":"finish off 结束，完成","headword":"finish off"},{"type":"entry","text":"final decision 最终决定","headword":"final decision"},{"type":"entry","text":"ultimate goal 最终目标","headword":"ultimate goal"},{"type":"entry","text":"brief summary 简单总结","headword":"brief summary"},{"type":"entry","text":"terminate the meeting 结束会议","headword":"terminate the meeting"},{"type":"entry","text":"go back to work 回去工作","headword":"go back to work"},{"type":"section","text":"Step2 学以致用"},{"type":"section","text":"Conversation 1"},{"type":"example","text":"A：You don't have to win every argument. Just agree to disagree.（你"},{"type":"text","text":"不必赢得每一场争论。求同存异吧。）"},{"type":"example","text":"B：I have to learn more. （我还得多学习。）"},{"type":"section","text":"Conversation 2"}]},{"number":1037,"blocks":[{"type":"example","text":"A：The meeting was positive and productive. （会议是积极且富有"},{"type":"text","text":"成效的。）"},{"type":"example","text":"B：Yes, it was successful. （是的，会议很成功。）"}]}]}